ofile.io/\">GoFile.io</a> - Free file sharing and storage platform, can be used via web based UI &#x26; also API. unlimited file size, bandwidth, download count, etc. But when a file becomes inactive (no download for more than 10 days), it will be deleted.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-10-09T10:28:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ripienaar/free-for-dev","categoryHTML":"<h2>Security and PKI</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/\">CyberChef</a> — A simple, intuitive web app for analysing and decoding/encoding data without having to deal with complex tools or programming languages. Like a swiss army knife of cryptography &#x26; encryption. All features are free to use, no limit. Open source, if you wish to self-host.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-10-09T10:16:31.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ripienaar/free-for-dev","categoryHTML":"<h2>Search</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.commandbar.com/\">CommandBar</a> - Unified Search Bar as-a-service, web based UI widget/plugin that allows your users to search contents, navigations, features, etc. within your product, which helps discoverability. Free for up-to 1000 Monthly Active Users, unlimited commands.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-10-09T10:00:29.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ripienaar/free-for-dev","categoryHTML":"<h2>Email</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://proton.me/mail\">Proton Mail</a> -  Free secure email account service provider with built-in end-to-end encryption. Free 1GB storage.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-10-09T09:43:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ripienaar/free-for-dev","categoryHTML":"<h2>Email</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tutanota.com/\">Tutanota</a> - Free secure email account service provider with built-in end-to-end encryption, no ads, no tracking. Free 1GB storage. Which also partially <a href=\"https://github.com/tutao/tutanota\">open source</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tutao/tutanota\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative